Text: EOL Directory Cc completed a audit of the current user access rights for the OEOL directory In our analysis we have determined that there are authorized users who no longer need access to this directory In order to better maintain the EOL directory we will be removing your access to the directory If there are business needs that require continued access please call Jennifer Denny at Thank you for your cooperation
